text: Pre-1927 Route 4 was a route in New Jersey that ran from Absecon north to Rahway, existing from 1916 to 1927. Today, it is part of the following routes: * U.S. Route 9 in New Jersey * New Jersey Route 88 * New Jersey Route 35 * New Jersey Route 71 * New Jersey Route 35 Category:U.S. Route 9 04 (pre-1927)
title: New Jersey Route 4 (pre-1927)
